&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor of Science (or greater) degree in Aerospace Engineering, Mechanical Engineering, or a similar engineering discipline.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least six (6) years of professional experience performing structural analysis on spacecraft or launch vehicle structures and components.&lt;/li&gt;
